converting into bins so that its easy to classify¶

In [26]:
bins=[0,3,6,9,12,15]
groups=['low','medium-low','medium','high','very high']
wine_white['fixed_acidity_bin']=pd.cut(wine_white['fixed acidity'],bins,labels=groups)
fixed_acidity_bin=pd.crosstab(wine_white['fixed_acidity_bin'],wine_white['quality'])
fixed_acidity_bin.div(fixed_acidity_bin.sum(1).astype(float),axis=0).plot(kind='bar',stacked=True,figsize=(10,10))
plt.xlabel('fixed_acidity_bin')
plt.ylabel('quality')
